I hope this certain enchanters views, trouble you as much as they trouble me.  I for one being an enchanter am embarrased at this persons views, and am forwarding his comments to VI with my recommendation that maybe they re-evaluate our spells/abilities, since if we can outdamage 5 of another class solo, then we are overpowered, and WE KNOW IT.<br>
<br>
We wouldn't like it if clerics could outdamage us, why should we be allowed to outdamage entire groups (even if it's a melee heavy group).  Then to make fun of a class that lost their solo ability and has had more difficulty getting into groups than we have ever had, it's not about us, it's about the integrity of the game and consistancy (as one mage put it).<br>
