An Ench can outdamage a wiz in dps.  YES. <br>
A charmed mob damn well better be able to outdo others.. they are TEMPORARY, and come with significant RISK. A wiz's dps are constant.. they will always have them, and they will always be protected behind a snare. Survival mechanism built in. I would gladly drop some dps for a protective snare.. any day of the week.<br>
<br>
Chanters can make mad AA. YES - IF we could charm them without risk, but the dps that makes them unbalancing can VERY easily mutilate a chanter in a VERY short time. But I think you better look at the mobs and talk to them about it. We're just using what is around, just like charm always has. Its not our fault that VI has gone totally insane and blown EQ totally out of proportion. charm power ONLY scales directly with the mobs faced.. it can't really do anything else.<br>
<br>
BUT if we can make such mad AA, why to all the druids and Wiz in our guild have 100-200+ AA's? Not many chanters I even know of have 100+.<br>
<br>
So we get TEMPORARY uberness for SIGNIFICANT risk, with no survival mechanisms built in. (and no, arcane rune, mez, and slow aren't a survival mech against a charm. AR is pulverized in one round - the same round which easily stuns, or interrupts casting Mez, and you generally don't slow your charms) So you may get lucky channeling, and sustain a pet for a while, but the odds are not in your favor with a 6-800 hitter.<br>
<br>
Without charms, our DPS is laughable. This is our tradeoff. WE take risks, we get a bigger reward than a wiz with uber nukes, and a snare, (same for druids), or a mage with a pet that has 2-3X the hp our summons do, and who can heal the pet as well. <br>
<br>
Leave our charms alone. We've put up with enough crap in the past. There is no need to nerf a class, due to a VERY small percentage of ppl killing a highly visible mob, and pissing ppl off. Many chanters will never see those zones or spell for a long time. Don't take away the few things they have to look forward to.<br>
<br>
So we're down to the original whines.. Chanters are stealing our BoT minis.. <br>
<br>
WELL - Stick an AE 1 or 2 slot dispell on the minis'<br>
<br>
GEEE that cures the use of charms agains minis.. and shouldn't affect too many ppls fights... we should all remember the days of carrying an insta clicky for that very reason.<br>
<br>
Hymay<br>
